    "description": "Grow your career with MobiKwik Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Risk Analyst for our Kolkata team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout MobiKwik Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMobiKwik Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in GST\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MobiKwik Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
